<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Inspiration Travel | Event Details</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --navy: #163a70;
      --gold: #caa85c;
      --bg: #f7f8fb;
      --text: #1f2937;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --line: #e5e7eb;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(22,58,112,.95), rgba(22,58,112,.8));
      color: white;
      padding: 56px 20px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      font-size: 12px;
      opacity: .85;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    h1, h2, h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .hero p {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin-bottom: 0;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .meta {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .meta-card, .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.04);
    }

    .meta-card strong {
      display: block;
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-size: 13px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .04em;
    }

    main {
      padding: 28px 20px 48px;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      gap: 22px;
    }

    .section + .section {
      margin-top: 22px;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--navy);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-right: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .button.secondary {
      background: white;
      color: var(--navy);
      border: 1px solid var(--navy);
    }

    .notice {
      background: #fff8eb;
      border: 1px solid #f2dfb6;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 16px;
    }

    .small {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 28px 20px 50px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 800px) {
      h1 { font-size: 30px; }
      .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="eyebrow">Inspiration Travel Event Page</div>
      <h1>Alaska Cruise 2026</h1>
      <p>We’re honored to welcome you on this upcoming journey. This page includes the most important details, planning reminders, and helpful links for your event.</p>

      <div class="meta">
        <div class="meta-card">
          <strong>Event Code</strong>
          IG26AE
        </div>
        <div class="meta-card">
          <strong>Sailing Dates</strong>
          June 14–21, 2026
        </div>
        <div class="meta-card">
          <strong>Ship</strong>
          [Ship Name]
        </div>
        <div class="meta-card">
          <strong>Embarkation Port</strong>
          Seattle, Washington
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="container grid">
      <div>
        <section class="card section">
          <h2>What You Need Right Now</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Complete online check-in when available.</li>
            <li>Review passport and travel documentation requirements.</li>
            <li>Note your final payment deadline.</li>
            <li>Watch for upcoming pre-departure emails from Inspiration Travel.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="card section">
          <h2>Important Dates</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Final Payment Due:</strong> May 18, 2026</li>
            <li><strong>Document Reminder:</strong> May 1, 2026</li>
            <li><strong>Embarkation Day:</strong> June 14, 2026</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="card section">
          <h2>Travel Preparation</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Bring a valid passport and required travel documents.</li>
            <li>Review packing recommendations for weather, excursions, and evening dining.</li>
            <li>Arrive at the port within your assigned check-in window.</li>
            <li>Keep medications, travel documents, and essentials in your carry-on bag.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="card section">
          <h2>Helpful Links</h2>
          <a class="button" href="#">Manage Booking</a>
          <a class="button secondary" href="#">Download Packing Guide</a>
          <a class="button secondary" href="#">View FAQ</a>
        </section>
      </div>

      <aside>
        <section class="card section">
          <h3>Need Assistance?</h3>
          <p>Our team is here to help as you prepare for your journey.</p>
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> [Support Email]<br />
          <strong>Phone:</strong> [Phone Number]</p>
          <p class="small">Business hours: [Hours]</p>
        </section>

        <section class="notice section">
          <h3>Important Note</h3>
          <p class="small">This page is intended for general event details only. Personal reservation information and payment-specific account details should remain in secure email or booking portals.</p>
        </section>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    Inspiration Travel • Event Information Page
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
